arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start()

	--Static Run from A to B
	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_BLOOD_STAG)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorClone) then	
		--Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(actorClone, 5)
		Hydra.QActorWait(actorClone, 2)
		--Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(actorClone, FX_BLOOD_BLAST)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone, 0.3)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorClone)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(LOC_TARGET_EG, 5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_TARGET_EG, FX_BLOOD_BLAST)

end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_STONE_CENTER, EG_BLOOD_STONE)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor ("DRUID_CLASSQ_SHRINE", idSelf, idSelf)
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("DRUID_BLOOD_POOL", idSelf, idSelf)
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_DRUID_CQUEST_BLOOD_STAG", idSelf, idSelf)
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	
	--Create Clone + Delete	
	bloodStag = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_BLOOD_STAG)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(bloodStag) then	
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(bloodStag, ANIM_SUMMON)
		Hydra.QActorWait(bloodStag, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(bloodStag, 0)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	stagReborn = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_REBORN_STAG)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(stagReborn) then	
		Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(stagReborn, 5)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(stagReborn, FX_SPIRIT_BLAST)
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(stagReborn, ANIM_SUMMON)
		Hydra.QActorWait(stagReborn, 3)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(stagReborn, 0)
	end
	
	Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idActorPlayer, "QST_Scos_Druid_Class_Quest_01_Fin_Gossip")
	
end

function Start()
	
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	druidClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_DRUID_NPC)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(druidClone) then	
		Hydra.QActorWait(druidClone, 1)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(druidClone, ANIM_CAST)
		Hydra.QActorWait(druidClone, 1)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_DRUID_FIN, id_Self, druidClone)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(druidClone, CONVO_DRUID_FIN)
		Hydra.QActorWait(druidClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(druidClone)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(druidClone, 1)
	end
	
end
